# Component Rules
- Prefer `const` arrow functions: `const MyComponent = () => {}`
- Named exports only
- Co-locate component-specific types in the same file
- Custom hooks go in `src/hooks/` and must start with `use`
- Avoid prop drilling — use Context or Zustand for deeply shared state
- Keep components pure where possible; side effects belong in hooks
- Use shadcn/ui primitives — never modify files in `components/ui/` directly